front.title: •Prepare The Chamber
front.gametext: USED: Add 2 to Carbon Freezing destiny.  LOST: If one of your Ugnaughts is defending in a battle, add one battle destiny.
front.lore: Coolant emitted by the TCF32 Carbonite Encasement Apparatus is rumored to have a mildly euphoric effect on Ugnaughts. Individuals on TCF32 duty are regarded with envy.

combo: Prepare the Chamber + Carbonite Chamber Console + 3 Ugnaughts + Carbon Freezing
